Package org.coniks.coniks_test_client Description

Provides the classes necessary to create a simple CONIKS test client, as well as the classes this clients uses to perform the CONIKS protocols with a CONIKS server.

This simple test client supports new key registrations, key lookups, key changes and key consistency checks. It is designed to communicate with the reference implementation of a CONIKS server.

Since:
1.1.0
